name: The Lynx Mod
desc:
A catboy NPC replacer! Replaces Vilia, the Hylian in drag, with a new friend that will soon make appearances in different places to sell The Hero new clothes!

To start the quest, just talk to the suspicious man outside of Gerudo Town like normal!
No new steps or stages were added to the quest, only dialogue changes have been made~
Dialogue in this mod is neutral so it can be used for any character!
